					</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/cablemanpunk/kandai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-electric-green transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
